===Noun===
#In music a '''pulse''' is periodically recurring short stimuli which are perceived as points in time. (DeLone et. al. (Eds.), 1975, chap. 3)
# A pulse can also refer to a class of [[vegetable]]s including [[pea]]s and [[bean]]s.

